{"name": "dagster-wandb", "metadata": {"name": "dagster-wandb", "version": "0.25.3", "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: Apache Software License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.9"], "home_page": "https://github.com/dagster-io/dagster/tree/master/python_modules/libraries/dagster-wandb", "license": "Apache-2.0", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["dagster", "wandb"], "summary": "Package for wandb Dagster components.", "upload_time": 1732224218}, "documentation": [""], "modules": [{"name": "dagster_wandb.launch", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "dagster_wandb.launch.configs", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "dagster_wandb.launch.configs.launch_config", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "dagster_wandb.launch.configs.launch_agent_config", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "dagster_wandb", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "dagster_wandb.run_launch_agent", "xref": {"fqname": "dagster_wandb.launch.ops.run_launch_agent", "project": null}}, {"name": "dagster_wandb.run_launch_job", "xref": {"fqname": "dagster_wandb.launch.ops.run_launch_job", "project": null}}, {"name": "dagster_wandb.SerializationModule", "xref": {"fqname": "dagster_wandb.types.SerializationModule", "project": null}}, {"name": "dagster_wandb.wandb_artifacts_io_manager", "xref": {"fqname": "dagster_wandb.io_manager.wandb_artifacts_io_manager", "project": null}}, {"name": "dagster_wandb.wandb_resource", "xref": {"fqname": "dagster_wandb.resources.wandb_resource", "project": null}}, {"name": "dagster_wandb.WandbArtifactConfiguration", "xref": {"fqname": "dagster_wandb.types.WandbArtifactConfiguration", "project": null}}, {"name": "dagster_wandb.WandbArtifactsIOManagerError", "xref": {"fqname": "dagster_wandb.io_manager.WandbArtifactsIOManagerError", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "dagster_wandb.launch.ops", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "dagster_wandb.launch.ops.raise_on_invalid_config", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "context", "type": {"name": "OpExecutionContext", "xref": {"fqname": "dagster.OpExecutionContext", "project": "dagster"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "dagster_wandb.launch.ops.run_launch_agent", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "context", "type": {"name": "OpExecutionContext", "xref": {"fqname": "dagster.OpExecutionContext", "project": "dagster"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["It starts a Launch Agent and runs it as a long running process until stopped manually.\n\nAgents are processes that poll launch queues and execute the jobs (or dispatch them to external\nservices to be executed) in order.\n\n**Example:**\n\n```YAML\n# config.yaml\n\nresources:\n  wandb_config:\n    config:\n      entity: my_entity\n      project: my_project\nops:\n  run_launch_agent:\n    config:\n      max_jobs: -1\n      queues:\n        - my_dagster_queue\n```\n\n```python\nfrom dagster_wandb.launch.ops import run_launch_agent\nfrom dagster_wandb.resources import wandb_resource\n\nfrom dagster import job, make_values_resource\n\n\n@job(\n    resource_defs={\n        \"wandb_config\": make_values_resource(\n            entity=str,\n            project=str,\n        ),\n        \"wandb_resource\": wandb_resource.configured(\n            {\"api_key\": {\"env\": \"WANDB_API_KEY\"}}\n        ),\n    },\n)\ndef run_launch_agent_example():\n    run_launch_agent()\n```\n"]}, {"name": "dagster_wandb.launch.ops.run_launch_job", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "context", "type": {"name": "OpExecutionContext", "xref": {"fqname": "dagster.OpExecutionContext", "project": "dagster"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Executes a Launch job.\n\nA Launch job is assigned to a queue in order to be executed. You can create a queue or use the\ndefault one. Make sure you have an active agent listening to that queue. You can run an agent\ninside your Dagster instance but can also consider using a deployable agent in Kubernetes.\n\n**Example:**\n\n```YAML\n# config.yaml\n\nresources:\n  wandb_config:\n    config:\n      entity: my_entity\n      project: my_project\nops:\n  my_launched_job:\n    config:\n      entry_point:\n        - python\n        - train.py\n      queue: my_dagster_queue\n      uri: https://github.com/wandb/example-dagster-integration-with-launch\n```\n\n```python\nfrom dagster_wandb.launch.ops import run_launch_job\nfrom dagster_wandb.resources import wandb_resource\n\nfrom dagster import job, make_values_resource\n\n\n@job(\n    resource_defs={\n        \"wandb_config\": make_values_resource(\n            entity=str,\n            project=str,\n        ),\n        \"wandb_resource\": wandb_resource.configured(\n            {\"api_key\": {\"env\": \"WANDB_API_KEY\"}}\n        ),\n    },\n)\ndef run_launch_job_example():\n    run_launch_job.alias(\"my_launched_job\")() # we rename the job with an alias\n```\n"]}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "dagster_wandb.version", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "dagster_wandb.version.__version__", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "dagster_wandb.resources", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "dagster_wandb.resources.wandb_resource", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "context", "type": {"name": "InitResourceContext", "xref": {"fqname": "dagster.InitResourceContext", "project": "dagster"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "Dict", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Dict", "project": "--